{"tid":1116321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台女遭強姦前發求救短訊　同學以為講笑無人理 結果成功中出","createTime":"2019-04-20T00:57:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T02:38:25.000Z","uid":72009,"like":77,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0daff6e1e3baf35968967a332e24f0cbc9c0e23b","tid":1116321,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T00:57:19.000Z","msg":"台灣高雄16歲少女小文2016年8月在街頭玩手機時，被騎車的張姓男子威脅性交，更稱反抗的話就將其殺死。小文因害怕遭遇不測，只好乖乖上車。小文在行車途中不斷用社交通訊軟件Line在群組求救，只可惜被同學當成玩笑話，最終還是被張男強姦。 <br />\n<br />\n事發後，小文以髮圈沾染對方的精液搜證，報警處理。案件於高雄法院審理，張男在法庭上否認犯行，辯稱他見小文心情不好才上前關心，詢問對方是否要發生性關係後，對方先拒絕後答應。他又指，小文要是不同意，可以半路逃跑，但她沒有這樣做。 <br />\n<br />\n法官認為，小文若是答應張男，就不會搜證、發短訊求救，還拍下張的車牌號碼，可以看出小文為求自保選擇配合，並非自願。加上張男是猥褻、強制性交等罪的積犯，遂依強制性交罪，將其重判7年有期徒刑。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190420/mobile/bkn-20190420081550408-0420_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190420%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190420081550408-0420_00952_001.html&d=v6UOKjiqNHu3M1gE0B2GLARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=22923c49\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190420/mobile/bkn-20190420081550408-0420_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11c6e985ef3a4c898a93803ae521920b9688578","tid":1116321,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T01:00:05.000Z","msg":"狼來了故事？"},{"pid":"7908d8b53bfda8c45e22ec63ec71407e4891d821","tid":1116321,"uid":38904,"like":56,"dislike":3,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T01:38:28.000Z","msg":"高雄終於有入球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d9ed001d548777b1835fb88b9aefe58c61fd0f","tid":1116321,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"ci